they have "ancient aliens s02e04" at filestube dot com

I started watching this serious and found the ancient alien theory plausible.  I then read and HIGHLY recommend "The Giza Power Plant" by Chris Dunn.  The author is a machinist and tool maker among other things for 49 years.  Through his machinist's eyes he recognized the signs and marks left over by power tools to cut the giza pyramid and so investigated and wrote a book.  It's full of jaw dropping precision.  The ceiling width of a room is measured and is the same at both ends to .0001 of an inch (a hair is .001).  Several rooms in fact.  The egyptions were supposedly using soft bronze tools yet they cut through the 2nd hardest substance Diorite.  The king's coffer is one piece of granite.  It's hollowed out!! It also is so precise it could've been cut out on a computer lazer table.  These people supposedly didn't have the wheel!  This book is filled with shit like this.  Check it out!
